  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: `geth version` \r\n1.10.1-stable-c2d2f4ed\r\n\r\nOS & Version: Windows/Linux/OSX\r\nLinux\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nGet pending transactions from local binance node, match the result I get from https://bsc-dataseed1.binance.org\r\nGet real pending transaction list\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nNumber of pending transactions is more less than expected (~2000), number of queued transactions is much more than expected (~13000). \r\nExample: local node does not give back new token listings on pancakeswap but data from https://bsc-dataseed1.binance.org seems valid.\r\nLocal node seems to be synchronized.\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\nusing web3 in python3.8\r\ngetting pending transaction filter id with 'eth_newPendingTransactionFilter' method (POST to local node or https://bsc-dataseed1.binance.org)\r\nusing 'eth_getFilterChanges' method with the pending filter id (POST to local node or https://bsc-dataseed1.binance.org)\r\n",
